{"timestamp": 1772630473.1762757, "task_id": "test-regen-timeout-001", "task_type": "code", "description": "生成包含 10000 行数据的复杂报告（故意制造超时）", "result": {"success": true, "agent": "coder", "duration": 11.911565780639648, "output": "我会为您生成一个包含10000行数据的复杂报告。让我创建一个Python脚本来生成这个报告。\n\n```python\nimport random\nimport datetime\nfrom typing import List, Dict\n\ndef generate_complex_report(num_rows: int = 10000) -> str:\n    \"\"\"生成包含复杂数据的报告\"\"\"\n    \n    # 报告头部\n    report = []\n    report.append(\"=\" * 100)\n    report.append(\"复杂数据分析报告\")\n    report.append(f\"生成时间: {datetime.datetime.now().strftime('%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')}\")\n    report.append(f\"数据行数: {num_rows}\")\n    report.append(\"=\" * 100)\n    report.append(\"\")\n    \n    # 列标题\n    report.append(f\"{'ID':<8} {'日期':<12} {'产品':<15} {'销售额':<12} {'数量':<8} {'地区':<10} {'状态':<10}\")\n    report.append(\"-\" * 100)\n    \n    # 数据生成\n    products = [\"笔记本电脑\", \"台式机\", \"显示器\", \"键盘\", \"鼠标\", \"耳机\", \"摄像头\", \"打印机\"]\n    regions = [\"华北\", \"华东\", \"华南\", \"西南\", \"东北\", \"西北\", \"华中\"]\n    statuses = [\"已完成\", \"处理中\", \"已取消\", \"待确认\"]\n    \n    for i in range(1, num_rows + 1):\n        date = datetime.date(2024, random.randint(1, 12), random.randint(1, 28))\n        product = random.choice(products)\n        amount = random.uniform(100, 50000)\n        quantity = random.randint(1, 100)\n        region = random.choice(regions)\n        status = random.choice(statuses)\n        \n        report.append(\n            f\"{i:<8} {date.strftime('%Y-%m-%d'):<12} {product:<15} \"\n            f\"{amount:>10.2f}元 {quantity:<8} {region:<10} {status:<10}\"\n        )\n    \n    # 统计摘要\n    report.append(\"\")\n    report.append(\"=\" * 100)\n    report.append(\"统计摘要\")\n    report.append(\"=\" * 100)\n    report.append(f\"总记录数: {num_rows}\")\n    report.append(f\"产品类型: {len(products)}\")\n    report.append(f\"覆盖地区: {len(regions)}\")\n    report.append(\"\")\n    \n    return \"\\n\".join(report)\n\n# 生成报告\nreport_content = generate_complex_report(10000)\n\n# 保存到文件\nwith open(\"complex_report_10000.txt\", \"w\", encoding=\"utf-8\") as f:\n    f.write(report_content)\n\nprint(f\"报告已生成，共 {len(report_content.splitlines())} 行\")\nprint(f\"文件大小: {len(report_content)} 字节\")\n```\n\n这个脚本会生成一个包含10000行销售数据的复杂报告，包括：\n- ID、日期、产品名称、销售额、数量、地区和状态\n- 随机生成的真实感数据\n- 报告头部和统计摘要\n\n报告将保存为 `complex_report_10000.txt` 文件。您可以运行这个脚本来生成报告。", "tokens": {"input": 3082, "output": 844}}, "retry_count": 0, "total_attempts": 1}
