{"timestamp": 1772749875.2553616, "task_id": "task-test-1772712611423-af1166", "task_type": "monitor", "description": "生成资源使用趋势图", "result": {"success": true, "agent": "monitor", "duration": 21.030452489852905, "output": "我会帮你创建一个资源使用趋势图的工具。让我先检查一下当前的系统状态，然后生成一个可以监控和可视化资源使用趋势的脚本。\n\n<get_diagnostics>\n<path>.</path>\n</get_diagnostics>\n\n<list_directory>\n<path>.</path>\n<recursive>false</recursive>\n</list_directory>\n\n现在我将创建一个资源监控脚本，可以收集系统资源使用数据并生成趋势图：\n\n<write_file>\n<path>resource_monitor.py</path>\n<content>#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"\n系统资源使用趋势监控工具\n实时收集CPU、内存、磁盘使用数据并生成可视化趋势图\n\"\"\"\n\nimport psutil\nimport time\nimport matplotlib.pyplot as plt\nfrom datetime import datetime\nfrom collections import deque\nimport matplotlib.dates as mdates\n\nclass ResourceMonitor:\n    def __init__(self, max_points=60):\n        self.max_points = max_points\n        self.timestamps = deque(maxlen=max_points)\n        self.cpu_usage = deque(maxlen=max_points)\n        self.memory_usage = deque(maxlen=max_points)\n        self.disk_usage = deque(maxlen=max_points)\n        \n    def collect_data(self):\n        \"\"\"收集当前系统资源使用数据\"\"\"\n        self.timestamps.append(datetime.now())\n        self.cpu_usage.append(psutil.cpu_percent(interval=1))\n        self.memory_usage.append(psutil.virtual_memory().percent)\n        self.disk_usage.append(psutil.disk_usage('/').percent)\n        \n    def generate_plot(self, filename='resource_trend.png'):\n        \"\"\"生成资源使用趋势图\"\"\"\n        fig, (ax1, ax2, ax3) = plt.subplots(3, 1, figsize=(12, 10))\n        fig.suptitle('系统资源使用趋势', fontsize=16, fontweight='bold')\n        \n        times = list(self.timestamps)\n        \n        # CPU使用率\n        ax1.plot(times, list(self.cpu_usage), 'b-', linewidth=2, label='CPU使用率')\n        ax1.fill_between(times, list(self.cpu_usage), alpha=0.3)\n        ax1.set_ylabel('CPU使用率 (%)', fontsize=12)\n        ax1.set_ylim(0, 100)\n        ax1.grid(True, alpha=0.3)\n        ax1.legend(loc='upper left')\n        \n        # 内存使用率\n        ax2.plot(times, list(self.memory_usage), 'g-', linewidth=2, label='内存使用率')\n        ax2.fill_between(times, list(self.memory_usage), alpha=0.3, color='green')\n        ax2.set_ylabel('内存使用率 (%)', fontsize=12)\n        ax2.set_ylim(0, 100)\n        ax2.grid(True, alpha=0.3)\n        ax2.legend(loc='upper left')\n        \n        # 磁盘使用率\n        ax3.plot(times, list(self.disk_usage), 'r-', linewidth=2, label='磁盘使用率')\n        ax3.fill_between(times, list(self.disk_usage), alpha=0.3, color='red')\n        ax3.set_ylabel('磁盘使用率 (%)', fontsize=12)\n        ax3.set_xlabel('时间', fontsize=12)\n        ax3.set_ylim(0, 100)\n        ax3.grid(True, alpha=0.3)\n        ax3.legend(loc='upper left')\n        \n        # 格式化时间轴\n        for ax in [ax1, ax2, ax3]:\n            ax.xaxis.set_major_formatter(mdates.DateFormatter('%H:%M:%S'))\n            plt.setp(ax.xaxis.get_majorticklabels(), rotation=45)\n        \n        plt.tight_layout()\n        plt.savefig(filename, dpi=150, bbox_inches='tight')\n        print(f\"趋势图已保存到: {filename}\")\n        \n    def print_current_status(self):\n        \"\"\"打印当前系统状态\"\"\"\n        if not self.timestamps:\n            return\n            \n        print(f\"\\n{'='*60}\")\n        print(f\"时间: {self.timestamps[-1].strftime('%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')}\")\n        print(f\"{'='*60}\")\n        print(f\"CPU使用率:  {self.cpu_usage[-1]:.1f}%\")\n        print(f\"内存使用率: {self.memory_usage[-1]:.1f}%\")\n        print(f\"磁盘使用率: {self.disk_usage[-1]:.1f}%\")\n        print(f\"{'='*60}\\n\")\n\ndef main():\n    monitor = ResourceMonitor(max_points=60)\n    \n    print(\"开始监控系统资源使用情况...\")\n    print(\"将收集60个数据点（约60秒），然后生成趋势图\")\n    print(\"按 Ctrl+C 可提前停止\\n\")\n    \n    try:\n        for i in range(60):\n            monitor.collect_data()\n            monitor.print_current_status()\n            print(f\"进度: {i+1}/60\")\n            time.sleep(1)\n            \n    except KeyboardInterrupt:\n        print(\"\\n\\n监控已停止\")\n    \n    finally:\n        if len(monitor.timestamps) > 0:\n            monitor.generate_plot()\n            print(\"\\n监控完成！\")\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    main()\n</content>\n</write_file>\n\n<write_file>\n<path>requirements.txt</path>\n<content>psutil>=5.9.0\nmatplotlib>=3.5.0\n</content>\n</write_file>\n\n<write_file>\n<path>README_monitor.md</path>\n<content># 系统资源使用趋势监控工具\n\n## 功能\n- 实时监控CPU、内存、磁盘使用率\n- 自动生成可视化趋势图\n- 支持中文显示\n\n## 安装依赖\n```bash\npip install -r requirements.txt\n```\n\n## 使用方法\n```bash\npython resource_monitor.py\n```\n\n脚本将运行60秒，每秒收集一次数据，最后生成 `resource_trend.png` 趋势图。\n\n## 输出\n- 实时控制台输出：显示当前资源使用情况\n- PNG图表文件：包含CPU、内存、磁盘使用率的时间序列图\n</content>\n</write_file>\n\n已创建资源监控工具。运行 `pip install -r requirements.txt` 安装依赖，然后执行 `python resource_monitor.py` 即可开始监控并生成趋势图。", "tokens": {"input": 3998, "output": 1417}}, "retry_count": 0, "total_attempts": 1}
